因为命运我嫁给了马丁 买了有棵死树的房子
Because of fate I married Martin and bought the house with the dead tree.

481
00:46:32,650 --> 00:46:36,900
所以离婚了
On account of which I got divorced and hit a car...

482
00:46:37,070 --> 00:46:40,490
还害我撞车遇上瑞克
...and met Rick, while buying a neck brace.

483
00:46:40,660 --> 00:46:44,280
等等，你没有提过 你离婚是因为死树
You got divorced because of a tree?

484
00:46:44,460 --> 00:46:47,870
-是园丁 -你爱上园丁？
- The tree man. - You fell in love with him?

485
00:46:48,040 --> 00:46:54,080
我没说爱，我有说吗？ 我最爱看这段
I did not say love. This is my favorite part.

486
00:46:55,220 --> 00:47:01,560
-现在或者永无机会 -永无是个可怕的字眼
- It's now or never. - Never is a frightening word.

487
00:47:01,720 --> 00:47:06,260
错过幸福，我们就是傻子
We'd be fools to let happiness pass us by.

488
00:47:07,480 --> 00:47:12,600
没有温暖回忆的 冬季多冷啊
Winter must be cold for those with no warm memories.

489
00:47:13,900 --> 00:47:17,940
我们已错过春天
We've already missed the spring.

490
00:47:19,030 --> 00:47:24,070
-男人就是看不懂这部戏 -我知道
- Men never get this movie. - I know.

491
00:47:25,080 --> 00:47:27,820
