Mummy! Mummy!

492
00:47:30,090 --> 00:47:36,830
-妈咪！ -别怕，我在这儿
- Mummy! - It's okay. I'm here. I'm coming.

493
00:47:38,850 --> 00:47:43,010
没事了，梦到什么？
It's okay. What was that about?

494
00:47:43,180 --> 00:47:48,680
房子在下沉，水从窗子灌进来
Our house was sinking. There was water coming in all the windows.

495
00:47:50,280 --> 00:47:55,020
现在没事了
Well, it's okay now.

496
00:47:56,160 --> 00:48:02,370
现在怎么办？你做噩梦时 你妈都唱歌给你听
What shall we do? Your mother sang to you when you had bad dreams.

497
00:48:03,290 --> 00:48:07,080
唱“再见，黑鸟”
"Bye Bye Blackbird."

498
00:48:08,630 --> 00:48:13,710
我想她 人死后会怎样？
I miss her. What happens to someone after they die?

499
00:48:15,220 --> 00:48:20,130
-我不知道 -你相信有天堂吗？
- I don't know. - Do you believe in heaven?

500
00:48:22,430 --> 00:48:29,180
从不信还有来生 但现在不确定了
I never believed in an afterlife. But now, I don't know.

501
00:48:29,900 --> 00:48:36,270
因为我梦到… 你妈
Because I've had these dreams about your mum.

502
00:48:37,370 --> 00:48:42,490
我们谈了很久 谈你的情况
We have long talks... about you.

503
00:48:42,660 --> 00:48:48,950
她好像都知道 但我还是告诉她了
How you're doing. She sort of knows, but I tell her anyway.

504
00:48:49,130 --> 00:48:55,550
那怎么解释？ 有点像来生吧？
So what is that? It's sort of an afterlife, isn't it?

505
00:48:56,590 --> 00:48:59,760
我开始忘记她了
I'm starting to forget her.

506
00:49:14,610 --> 00:49:19,480
她会削苹果
She could peel an apple...

507
00:49:19,660 --> 00:49:23,290
皮都不断
...in one long, curly strip.

508
