- I love you, Jonah.  - I love you, Dad.

515
00:49:49,770 --> 00:49:51,690
?Where somebody waits for me ?

516
00:49:51,740 --> 00:49:54,820
明天见
See you tomorrow.

517
00:49:55,440 --> 00:49:59,160
?Sugar sweet so is she ?

518
