00:50:52,000 --> 00:50:54,340
?Blackbird ?

528
00:50:54,710 --> 00:50:56,300
?Lord have mercy ?

529
00:50:57,970 --> 00:51:02,390
?Wait for me darling, yeah ?

530
00:51:07,190 --> 00:51:13,020
劳莉吗？我是安妮 我很好
Laurie? It's Annie. I'm fine.

531
