How do I look? Do I look all right?

552
00:53:47,400 --> 00:53:52,890
我一副急于讨好的蠢样 该去理个发
I look stupid. I'm trying too hard. I was going to get a haircut.

553
00:53:53,070 --> 00:53:57,860
-这封信很好 -鞋跟的形状好奇怪
- This is a good letter, Dad. - These heels are grotesque.

554
00:53:58,030 --> 00:54:01,070
她叫安妮·瑞德
Her name is Annie Reed.

555
00:54:01,250 --> 00:54:04,780
爸，你看嘛
Dad, read this.

556
00:54:06,420 --> 00:54:10,500
“夜未眠父子…
"Dear Sleepless and Son...

557
00:54:10,670 --> 00:54:15,290
我是杰出三垒手 说到这个
I'm an excellent third baseman, and let me tell you...

558
00:54:15,470 --> 00:54:20,300
罗宾斯是最棒的三垒手 我是老乡当然无异议”
...Robinson was the best. We must agree on this. I'm from Baltimore."

559
00:54:20,470 --> 00:54:25,720
她跟你一样喜欢罗宾斯 这是个好预兆
She likes Brooks Robinson. So do you. It's a sign.

560
00:54:25,900 --> 00:54:30,510
过来，我教你什么叫预兆
Come here. I'll show you a sign.

561
00:54:33,240 --> 00:54:39,530
西雅图在哪？ 对，巴尔的摩呢？这边
Where's Seattle? And Baltimore? Right there!

562
00:54:39,700 --> 00:54:44,950
中间隔26州，这是啥预兆？
There's like 26 states between here and there. That's a sign.

563
00:54:45,120 --> 00:54:50,160
我走了，晚安，我爱你
I'm out of here. Goodbye. I love you.

564
00:54:53,090 --> 00:54:57,630
克莉斯，你车移开了吗？
Clarise, did you move your car?

565
00:55:05,190 --> 00:55:10,270
-谢谢，我要… -白酒？
- Thanks, Derrick. I'll have... - White wine spritzer?

566
00:55:10,440 --> 00:55:13,860
-你呢？ -不用
- And you, sir? - I'm fine.

567
00:55:14,030 --> 00:55:19,020
-你很漂亮 -你也很英俊
- You look good. - So do you.

568
00:55:22,250 --> 00:55:25,360
我以为你永远不会打给我
I thought you'd never call me.

569
00:55:25,540 --> 00:55:28,830
我好希望你会
I really wanted you to.

570
00:55:29,000 --> 00:55:34,870
鲍德温先生，你的电话
Mr. Baldwin, phone call for you.

571
00:55:41,520 --> 00:55:46,810
-爸，我们情人节去纽约好吗？ -什么？
Dad, can we go to New York for Valentine's Day?

572
00:55:46,980 --> 00:55:52,980
安妮约我们情人节在 帝国大厦顶楼见
Annie Reed wants to meet us at the top of the Empire State Building.

573
00:55:53,150 --> 00:56:00,150
乔纳，你跌倒流血了吗？ 克莉斯被勒死了吗？
Jonah, have you fallen down? Has Clarise been strangled?

574
00:56:00,330 --> 00:56:03,410
-没有啊 -你就为了问这事？
- No. - Is that the reason you're calling?

575
00:56:03,580 --> 00:56:08,920
现在订机票比较便宜 杰西卡父母开旅行社
We can get cheap tickets from Jessica's parents.

576
00:56:09,090 --> 00:56:13,330
现在没空 以后再说
We'll talk about it later.

577
00:56:13,510 --> 00:56:18,670
根本不该和你聊 去睡觉
This conversation has lasted too long. Go to bed.

578
00:56:24,310 --> 00:56:28,680
-没问题吧？ -你有孩子吗？
- Everything all right? - Yes. Do you have kids?

579
00:56:28,860 --> 00:56:32,070
我的送你好吗？
You want mine?

580
00:56:32,940 --> 00:56:37,190
我喝纯伏特加
I'll have an Absolut straight up.

581
00:56:53,840 --> 00:56:57,500
放下，别玩
Put that down. Stop it!

582
00:56:57,680 --> 00:57:01,800
-她来了 -她干嘛买菜？
- There she is. - Why is she bringing groceries?

583
00:57:01,980 --> 00:57:07,060
-她要做菜给我们吃 -嗨！山姆，谢谢
- She's going to cook for us. - Hi, Sam.

584
00:57:07,230 --> 00:57:11,270
我猜你一定是乔纳
Let me guess. You must be Jonah.

585
00:57:14,150 --> 00:57:18,610
就这些吗？ 车子在那边
This is it? The car is this way.

586
00:57:18,780 --> 00:57:25,700
她重漆六次 现在她又要重做火炉
She's on her sixth painter. And now she wants the fireplace rebricked.

587
00:57:25,880 --> 00:57:32,420
-我跟她很熟，我去劝她 -我有办法，用砖敲她
- I know her. I could call her. - I'll just hit her with a brick.

588
00:57:34,930 --> 00:57:37,960
好好笑，你好风趣
That's so funny. You're so funny.

589
00:57:38,140 --> 00:57:44,180
每次她想改装就说 “我很笨，你是专家
When she wants something done she says: "You know best.

590
00:57:44,350 --> 00:57:49,600
但房子前后 能否颠倒过来？
But couldn't we flip the house so the back is in front?

591
00:57:49,770 --> 00:57:55,860
前门上绞链 以便遥控开车库门”
Put the front on a hinge so I can get in with a garage door opener."

592
00:57:56,030 --> 00:58:02,320
-“我说可以，只要…” -“把橱柜移开”
- "Yes, we can. We'll just..." - "Move the cabinets."

593
00:58:09,500 --> 00:58:13,250
乔纳，点心拿过来
Jonah, bring some of that stuff.

594
00:58:13,420 --> 00:58:16,460
你喜欢棒球吗？
Do you like baseball?

595
00:58:16,640 --> 00:58:21,550
喜欢，我公司有水手队的包厢 不如大家去看一场
Yes. In fact my firm has box seats to the Mariners. Let's go some day.

596
00:58:23,270 --> 00:58:28,100
露营呢？你喜欢吗？
What about camping? Do you like that?

597
00:58:28,270 --> 00:58:31,060
我去露营过一次
I went camping once.

598
00:58:31,230 --> 00:58:36,980
-爸，我们应该常去露营 -对，露营很好，睡觉了
- We should go camping more often. - You're right. Time for bed.

599
00:58:37,160 --> 00:58:41,740
-才十点 -对，该睡了
- It's only 10:00. - That's right. Time for bed.

600
00:58:41,910 --> 00:58:44,900
晚安
Goodnight.

601
00:58:46,540 --> 00:58:50,540
不谢谢 维多莉亚做的好菜吗？
Thank Victoria for the nice dinner.

602
00:58:50,710 --> 00:58:55,800
谢谢你的晚餐 我从没看过有人这么煮土豆
Thanks for dinner. I never saw anybody cook potatoes that way.

603
00:58:55,970 --> 00:59:01,710
你喜欢就好，晚安
I'm glad you liked it. Goodnight, Jonah.

604
00:59:03,020 --> 00:59:08,980
我们很少吃土豆 我们吃米
We don't see a lot of potatoes here. We're rice men.

605
01:00:02,500 --> 01:00:05,740
抱歉，华特
I'm sorry, Walter. I'm sorry.

606
01:00:10,460 --> 01:00:13,080
打开收音机
Turn on your radio.

607
01:00:13,260 --> 01:00:18,250
又是那小鬼 你害我听这烂节目
The kid is on. You've got me listening to this garbage!

608
01:00:19,180 --> 01:00:26,270
是贝琪，她又跟瑞克吵架 贝琪，我再打过去
Becky's having trouble with Rick. Becky, I'll call you back.

609
01:00:29,110 --> 01:00:33,600
对不起，华特 流血了吗？
I'm sorry, Walter. Are you bleeding?

610
01:00:52,800 --> 01:00:55,960
他正在亲她
He's kissing her right now!

611
01:00:56,140 --> 01:00:59,920
乔纳，你在监视你父亲
Are you spying on your father?

612
01:01:00,100 --> 01:01:05,140
-他在亲谁？ -我要阻止他们
- Who is he kissing? - I have to make them stop.

613
01:01:05,310 --> 01:01:09,430
-叫我怎么向华特解释？ -她做晚餐
- How will I explain this to Walter? - She made dinner.

614
01:01:09,610 --> 01:01:12,820
她买了两大包的菜 可以吃一年了
She brought food for a whole year!

615
01:01:12,990 --> 01:01:17,480
你父亲约会那很好呀 你只是受不了
It's good that your father's dating. It's just hard on you.

616
01:01:17,660 --> 01:01:22,030
事情真如你所愿时 你吓坏了
You think you want it, but when it happens, it scares you.

617
01:01:22,200 --> 01:01:27,670
合不合适该由你爸决定
Shouldn't your father decide whether someone is right for him?

618
01:01:27,840 --> 01:01:30,120
他现在神智不清
He's not sane enough.

619
01:01:30,300 --> 01:01:36,170
他在吻她的唇 她是烂货，我爸被烂货勾引
He's kissing her on the lips. My dad's been captured by a 'ho!

620
01:01:36,340 --> 01:01:41,050
冷静点 明早吃早餐时
Calm down. Tomorrow, when you're having breakfast...

621
01:01:41,220 --> 01:01:47,090
再和你父亲谈 别闷在心里
...tell him how you feel. Don't keep it inside.

622
01:01:51,650 --> 01:01:56,240
拿着收音机 躲在清洁柜里
Miss Scarlett. In the broom closet. With the radio.

623
01:01:56,410 --> 01:02:01,950
华特，你吓死我了，下次不准这样
Walter, you scared me. Don't ever do that again.

624
01:02:04,830 --> 01:02:09,580
-我以为有只黑寡妇蜘蛛 -你把我和维多莉亚吓个半死
- I saw a black widow. - You scared me and Victoria.

625
01:02:09,750 --> 01:02:14,710
-本来在那里啊 -下次再看到黑寡妇就说
- It was right there. - Next time I want you to say:

626
01:02:14,880 --> 01:02:19,170
“爸，打扰了 我看到有毒昆虫”
"Dad, I see a poisonous insect."

627
01:02:19,350 --> 01:02:22,810
我就会来，别再大叫了
And I'll deal with it. Don't scream.

628
01:02:22,980 --> 01:02:27,470
贝琪以为电台 有个人是瑞克
Becky thought Rick was on the radio.

629
01:02:27,650 --> 01:02:33,560
结果是个住德鲁市的人 德鲁在哪？
It turned out the guy lived in Duluth. Where's Duluth?

630
01:02:33,740 --> 01:02:38,200
-这没道理 -我知道毫无道理
- That doesn't make any sense. - I know. No sense at all.

631
01:02:38,370 --> 01:02:44,080
-感谢主我生活有序 -德鲁在北达科他州
- Thank God my life is in place. - Duluth? That's in North Dakota.

632
01:02:58,430 --> 01:03:03,340
-我喜欢这封信，你该回信 -你觉得吗？
- Great letter. Write to her. - You think so?

633
01:03:03,520 --> 01:03:09,010
是YOH 你唯一的希望
It's Y-O-H. Your only hope.

634
01:03:20,740 --> 01:03:26,160
我要写电台节目报导
I thought I'd do a story on those radio shows.

635
01:03:26,330 --> 01:03:30,950
-也许还要实地研究 -没错
- You'd have to go somewhere. - Definitely.

636
01:03:49,860 --> 01:03:54,230
-不能电话采访吗？ -这篇不行
- Can't you do a phone interview? - No.

637
01:03:54,400 --> 01:03:58,690
-我不会在芝加哥待太久 -你回来时我已经走了
- I won't be in Chicago long. - When you get back, I'll be gone.

638
01:03:58,870 --> 01:04:02,990
-那就纽约见 -我来开
- Then I'll see you in New York. - I'll get it.

639
